We launched this survey in early February 2015. For 2 weeks, we ran ads for the survey on Stack Over
flow, shared the survey on Meta, and promoted it across social media.
These results are not scientific. They are skewed by selection bias and language bias and probably a few
other biases. So take this for what it is: possibly the most definitive developer survey on Earth. Or at least
the only survey that asks devs about tabs vs. spaces.
